'''2014年昆明火车站暴力恐怖袭击事件'''是於2014年3月1日21時许在[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]][[云南省|云南省]][[昆明市|昆明市]][[昆明站|昆明火车站]]发生的一起由[[新疆维吾尔自治区|新疆]][[恐怖分子|恐怖分子]]组织策划<ref name="xinhua" /><ref name="外交部">{{cite news|url =http://news.qq.com/a/20140303/021229.htm?pgv_ref=aio2012&ptlang=2052|title =外交部：昆明暴恐事件现场发现了“东突”旗帜|publisher =腾讯新闻|date =2014-03-03|dead-url =no|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140309063803/http://news.qq.com/a/20140303/021229.htm?pgv_ref=aio2012&ptlang=2052|archive-date =2014-03-09|access-date =2014-03-03}}</ref>的砍殺无辜平民的[[恐怖袭击|恐怖袭击]]事件。此案共造成平民31人死亡、141人受伤。3月3日下午，官方宣布破案，作案团伙共8人，5名直接参与袭击者中4人被当场击毙，1人被当场击伤抓获，其余3名策划者早於2月27日在云南省[[红河哈尼族彝族自治州|红河州]][[个旧市|个旧市]][[沙甸镇|沙甸镇]]被拘捕。同年9月12日，此案由云南省昆明市中级人民法院审理完毕并宣判<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://kmzy.chinacourt.org/article/detail/2014/09/id/1437791.shtml|title =昆明中院对“3·01”严重暴恐案当庭宣判|author =昆明中院|date =2014-09-12|publisher =昆明中院新闻中心|access-date =2014-09-23|quote =2014年9月12日下午，云南省昆明市中级人民法院对“3·01”昆明火车站严重暴力恐怖案件一审公开开庭审理完毕并当庭宣判|dead-url =no|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141211020011/http://kmzy.chinacourt.org/article/detail/2014/09/id/1437791.shtml|archive-date =2014-12-11}}</ref>。

== 經過 ==
=== 事件开端 ===
2014年3月1日晚21时20分，5名（事件发生后不久曾被误作十余名、八名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2014_03/03/34349607_0.shtml |title=10余名暴徒统一着装 |access-date=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2014-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303224400/http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2014_03/03/34349607_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>）统一着黑色服装的[[东突厥斯坦独立运动|东突分裂新疆势力]]男女持械衝入昆明火车站广场、售票厅，见人就砍，造成多人伤亡<ref name="xinhua" />。警方赶到现场后，对火车站实施封锁<ref>{{cite news |url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-01/231829598369.shtml |title = 民警对昆明火车站实施三层封锁 |publisher = 昆明电视台K6春城频道 |date = 2014-03-01 |dead-url = no |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140305142710/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-01/231829598369.shtml |archive-date = 2014-03-05 |access-date = 2014-03-01 }}</ref>。在[[中华人民共和国人民警察|警察]]使用三次[[催泪弹|催泪弹]]无效後<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/140229602259.shtml |title=目击者:昆明警方使用催泪枪无效后击毙暴徒 |access-date=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029141339/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/140229602259.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[北京路_(昆明)|北京路]]永平路交叉口当场击毙4名恐怖分子（3男1女）、击伤抓获1人（女）。
被当场抓获的女性凶徒肩部中弹<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2014/03-02/5899660.shtml|title =目击者讲述：警察向歹徒喊话“你们几个来砍我”|access-date =2014-03-09|author =史广林|date =2014-03-02|publisher =中国新闻社|quote =警察朝天鸣枪示警，五人仍然胡乱挥舞着手中的刀不断挑衅。随后赶来的特警开枪，四名歹徒倒地。一名蒙着头巾的女性歹徒仍然不放下凶器，被警方击中肩甲处，倒在地上。|dead-url =no|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140310021825/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2014/03-02/5899660.shtml|archive-date =2014-03-10}}</ref>，送往医院救治。现场留下约300米长的血迹，伤者多集中在售票厅，大多为购票乘车的乘客<ref name="恢复">{{cite news|url =http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-01/232729598398.shtml|title =昆明火车站售票进站陆续恢复|publisher =云南信息报|date =2014-03-01|dead-url =no|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140305142618/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-01/232729598398.shtml|archive-date =2014-03-05|access-date =2014-03-01}}</ref>。

=== 伤亡情况 ===
此次袭击共造成31人死亡，141人受伤，其中40人重伤，另有4名歹徒被击毙。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-09-12/165330839210.shtml |title=昆明火车站暴恐案宣判：3人获死刑1人无期 |access-date=2014-09-12 |archive-date=2014-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915033117/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-09-12/165330839210.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>在遇害者中包括兩名车站保安员，伤者中亦包括7名民警<ref>{{cite news |url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/124729602141.shtml |title = 昆明暴恐案2名车站保安员殉职 7名民警受伤 |publisher = 新浪网 |date = 2014-03-02 |dead-url = no |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313032656/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/124729602141.shtml |archive-date = 2014-03-13 |access-date = 2014-03-03 }}</ref>。据媒体报道，有警察为了保护乘客，对歹徒喊道：“来砍我！”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2014_03/04/34398639_0.shtml |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-12-30 |archive-date=2019-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230094149/http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2014_03/04/34398639_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

3月2日凌晨，[[国家卫生与计划生育委员会|国家卫生与计划生育委员会]]派遣[[北京协和医院|北京协和医院]]、[[北京大学第三医院|北京大学第三医院]]、[[首都医科大学附属北京天坛医院|北京天坛医院]]和[[四川大学华西医院|四川大学华西医院]]的9名医疗专家赴昆明指导当地开展伤员救治<ref name="wsjs">{{cite web |url = http://www.nhfpc.gov.cn/yjb/s3586/201403/45b428cce5a04735b3f0d933b6a93a33.shtml |title = 卫生计生部门全力开展云南昆明火车站暴力恐怖案件医疗救援工作 |publisher = [[中华人民共和国国家卫生和计划生育委员会|中华人民共和国国家卫生和计划生育委员会]] |date = 2014-03-02 |access-date = 2014-03-01 |dead-url = yes |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140305035436/http://www.nhfpc.gov.cn/yjb/s3586/201403/45b428cce5a04735b3f0d933b6a93a33.shtml |archive-date = 2014-03-05 }}</ref>，并从北京和成都紧急调派四批医疗队、共27名专家，于2日全部抵达昆明，开展指导救援工作<ref>{{cite news |url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/233329604097.shtml |title = 27名专家赶赴昆明救治恐怖事件伤员 |publisher = 新华网 |date = 2014-03-02 |dead-url = no |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304102110/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/233329604097.shtml |archive-date = 2016-03-04 |access-date = 2014-03-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/012229604309.shtml|title = 近两千名医护人员参与昆明暴恐事件医疗救援|publisher = 人民网|date = 2014-03-02|dead-url = no|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180519180110/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/012229604309.shtml|archive-date = 2018-05-19|access-date = 2014-03-03}}</ref>。伤员分别收治在昆明的12家医院<ref name="wsjs" /><ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.chinanews.com/sh/2014/03-03/5900375.shtml |title = 昆明12所医院1916名医护人员全力救治143名伤者 |publisher = 云南日报 |date = 2014-03-03 |dead-url = no |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306163609/http://www.chinanews.com/sh/2014/03-03/5900375.shtml |archive-date = 2014-03-06 |access-date = 2014-03-03 }}</ref>。

=== 事后安全措施与应对 ===
事件发生后，原本应于昆明站停靠的列车被暂时安排到其他站点临时停靠，1日晚23时起，车站秩序陆续恢复<ref name="恢复" />。[[昆明长水国际机场|昆明长水国际机场]]也紧急提升安保级别<ref>{{cite web|url =http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20140302/11780996_0.shtml|title =昆明长水机场提高安保级别 秩序正常|publisher =中国新闻网|date =2014-03-02|dead-url =no|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140302051435/http://finance.ifeng.com/a/20140302/11780996_0.shtml|archive-date =2014-03-02|access-date =2014-03-02}}</ref>。
特警对当地维吾尔族聚居点大树营加强巡逻<ref>{{Cite news|url =http://www.huarenlife.com/news/show.php?itemid=1738#0-tsina-1-1796-397232819ff9a47a7b7e80a40613cfe1|title =宽容不再 昆明维族聚居区被持枪特警包围|publisher =华人生活网|date =2014-03-03|access-date =2014-03-03|archive-date =2014-12-11|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141211023140/http://www.huarenlife.com/news/show.php?itemid=1738#0-tsina-1-1796-397232819ff9a47a7b7e80a40613cfe1|dead-url =yes}}</ref>。
中国其它地区机场亦提升了安防等级，增加了防爆检查<ref name="airport">{{cite news |url = http://sky.news.sina.com.cn/2014-03-03/100849001.html |title = 我国各机场安检升级 旅客需提前两小时到达 |date = 2014-03-03 |agency = 新浪航空 |access-date = 2014-03-02 |dead-url = no |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140310030029/http://sky.news.sina.com.cn/2014-03-03/100849001.html |archive-date = 2014-03-10 }}</ref>。北京、海南、四川、广州等地也对重要场所、交通枢纽、学校等地加强警戒<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/134529609751.shtml |title=海南对重点区域及人群聚集场所启动武装巡逻 |work=[[中国新闻网|中国新闻网]] |via=[[新浪网|新浪网]] |date=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103416/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/134529609751.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/163129611073.shtml |title=四川警方提升社会治安防范等级 24小时值班备勤 |access-date=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111510/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/163129611073.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/151329602509.shtml |title=成都武警持枪在火车站执勤(组图) |access-date=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309080333/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-02/151329602509.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/134229609752.shtml |title=昆明全市学校加强戒备 特警荷枪实弹武装巡逻 |work=[[中国新闻网|中国新闻网]] |via=[[新浪网|新浪网]] |date=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2018-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519180110/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/134229609752.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
时值[[全国两会|全国两会]]，北京召开紧急会议，通报昆明发生的暴力恐怖事件，要求进一步加强首都安保。<ref>{{Cite news|url =http://news.qq.com/a/20140302/006687.htm|title =北京通报昆明暴力恐怖事件 部署加强两会安保|publisher =腾讯|date =2014-03-02|dead-url =no|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140305162112/http://news.qq.com/a/20140302/006687.htm|archive-date =2014-03-05|access-date =2014-03-02}}</ref>。

3月2日，昆明火车站秩序基本恢复，有[[武警|武警]]持枪驻守巡逻<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://slide.news.sina.com.cn/c/slide_1_55674_44919.html#p=1 |title=昆明火车站武警持枪执勤 |access-date=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306195305/http://slide.news.sina.com.cn/c/slide_1_55674_44919.html#p=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[中国红十字会|中国红十字会]]于当日上午派出工作组赴云南指导云南省红十字会开展应急生命救护，组织无偿献血，调遣心理救援队为受害者家属和受惊吓的群众进行心理疏导和知识传播<ref>{{Cite news|url =http://news.163.com/14/0302/14/9MBAMB7N00014JB6.html|title =中国红十字会工作组赴云南处理昆明暴力恐怖事件|publisher =网易|date =2014-03-02|dead-url =yes|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141029174232/http://news.163.com/14/0302/14/9MBAMB7N00014JB6.html|archive-date =2014-10-29|access-date =2014-03-02}}</ref>。
