包括“多地发生恐怖袭击”、“昆明医院先收钱再收治伤者”<ref>{{cite news|author =李萌|title =官方回应：恐怖袭击伤者救治“缴纳五万元押金”系谣言|url =http://news.xinhuanet.com/local/2014-03/03/c_119579948.htm|access-date =2014-03-03|work =新华网|date =2014-03-03|publisher =新华社|location =昆明|dead-url =no|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150402180105/http://news.xinhuanet.com/local/2014-03/03/c_119579948.htm|archive-date =2015-04-02}}</ref>、“云南[[红河州|红河州]]抓获多个恐怖分子”、“昆明[[长水机场|长水机场]]抓获2个新疆人”、“11名嫌犯名单被公佈”<ref>{{cite web |url = http://weibo.com/1618051664/Azfgi6gP0 |title=头条新闻的微博 |website=[[新浪微博|新浪微博]] |access-date = 2014-03-03 |archive-date = 2014-03-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306202710/http://weibo.com/1618051664/Azfgi6gP0 |dead-url = no }}</ref>、“一名嫌犯逃往[[贵阳|贵阳]]”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/132829609674.shtml |title=网传昆明暴恐案1名嫌犯逃往贵阳 警方辟谣 |access-date=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402135915/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2014-03-03/132829609674.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>等。事件中，共有45人被捕，處以行政拘留。

